1. Ja *čuvam* svoje ključeve u novčaniku. (I keep my keys in my wallet.)
2. Oni *čuvaju* novac u banci. (They keep their money in the bank.)
3. Ti *čuvaš* svoje tajne veoma dobro. (You keep your secrets very well.)
4. Kada *čuvate* dete, morate biti veoma pažljivi. (When you're babysitting, you have to be very careful.)
5. On *čuva* svoju zemlju od invazije. (He protects his country from invasion.)
6. Mi *čuvamo* tradiciju naših predaka. (We preserve the tradition of our ancestors.)
7. Vi *čuvate* taj dokument u fiokama? (Are you keeping that document in your drawers?)
8. Njih dvoje *čuvaju* tajnu zajedno. (The two of them keep the secret together.)
9. Ova kamera *čuva* sve snimljeno na memorijskoj kartici. (This camera saves everything recorded on the memory card.)
10. Upravnik zgrade *čuva* ključeve za sve stanare. (The building manager keeps keys for all tenants.)